query:
SELECT l.id, l.nome
FROM users u
JOIN gestores g ON u.id = g.userId
JOIN gestor_lojas gl ON g.id = gl.gestorId
JOIN lojas l ON gl.lojaId = l.id
WHERE u.name LIKE '%Carlos Eduardo%'
AND l.id NOT IN (
  SELECT COALESCE(lojaId, 0) FROM relatorios_analise_loja 
  WHERE analiseId = (SELECT MAX(id) FROM analises_fichas_servico)
)
ORDER BY l.nome;
